query: WITH entities AS (SELECT authentication_id, id FROM core_customers WHERE ((authentication_id IS NOT DISTINCT FROM $3) AND COALESCE(id < $2, true) OR COALESCE(authentication_id < $3, authentication_id IS NOT NULL)) ORDER BY authentication_id DESC NULLS LAST, id DESC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.authentication_id desc nulls last, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
